        <h2><span class="legal-num">01</span>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>These Terms and Conditions ("<strong>Terms</strong>") constitute a legally binding agreement between you ("<strong>Customer</strong>," "<strong>you</strong>," or "<strong>your</strong>") and Metegrity Inc. ("<strong>Metegrity</strong>," "<strong>we</strong>," "<strong>us</strong>," or "<strong>our</strong>") governing your access to and use of our software products, website, and related services (collectively, the "<strong>Services</strong>").</p>
