        <p>Metegrity provides asset integrity management software solutions designed for pipeline, facility, and infrastructure operators. Our product offerings include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Visions Enterprise</strong> — Our comprehensive asset integrity management platform for managing inspections, risk assessments, and compliance across your entire asset portfolio.</li>
          <li><strong>VISIONSGO</strong> — A mobile-first field data collection application that enables inspectors to capture and synchronize inspection data in real time.</li>
          <li><strong>Visions RBI (Risk-Based Inspection)</strong> — Advanced risk assessment tools that help you prioritize inspections based on quantitative risk analysis and industry standards.</li>
          <li><strong>Fugitive Emissions Management</strong> — Leak detection and repair (LDAR) management solutions to help you comply with environmental regulations and reduce emissions.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any aspect of the Services at any time, with reasonable notice to active subscribers where practicable.</p>
      </section>

